data.description: Back on the market due to buyers getting cold feet. Inspection report is available to buyers. WDO inspection was clean. Beautiful home in a beautiful neighborhood. This is terrific community where you OWN the land.  North River Estates is one of the smallest and nicest parks in Manatee and Sarasota Counties. This is a 2015 Jacobsen home with 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms.  This home has an open floor plan with rich colors that give it a warm feeling.  All appliances in the kitchen are stainless steel and it has a island for eating breakfast or a quick lunch.  The island has drawers for easy storage of cooking items. It also has a wheelchair lift if you need it.  Master bedroom is a good size and has an en-suite bathroom with a walk in shower and extra cabinets for storage.  Crown molding on the kitchen cabinets and in the rooms. Lots of windows give it an abundance of natural light. The HOA fee here is only 125.00 per month and includes the maintenance of the clubhouse, the large heated pool, the fitness room, and they cut the grass including yours.  There are many activities available to someone wanting to make new friends.  They have game night, pot luck suppers, movie night, birthday celebrations every month, and a coffee hour one Saturday a month. They celebrate all the holidays and even sing Christmas Carols at Christmas time.  Once a month the guys and the girls get together and go check out some of the local restaurants.  North River Estates is close to shopping, dining, the SRQ airport and the some of the most gorgeous beaches on the gulf coast.  Trade in that snow shovel for some suntan lotion and enjoy the Florida lifestyle!  The furniture is not included in the sale of the home and can be purchased separately.
